        "timestamp": "2019-04-05 08:19:37.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nAbout the tag: this is my proposal for the tagging scheme, it's an official way of tagging Centos images: name=centos, tag=<release> eg 'centos7'.\n\nThen in molecule.yml we would have:\n  image: molecule-${PREBUILD_PLATFORM_DISTRO:-centos}:${PREBUILD_DISTRO_VERSION:-centos7.6}\n\n\nAs for the Dockerfile - verified it with some already created uploads with molecule tests and it works even better that previous one.",
        "patchset_number": 1
